strings.Value: "That female back at the barbarian camp... strange. Smells funny. Walks funny. As if broken."
"I... well, it's a strange to say, but I agree. When I stood next to her I got goosebumps all over!"
"I didn't like that witch either. I don't care what she smells like, but I don't trust those who hide their faces."
"Broken. Hmmm... that's an interesting notion from a degenerate pet like you. I wonder how close to the truth that is..."
